create_torrent 0.1.6 (Mon, 16 Jan 2017 15:51:50 -0500):
	new option -gray for grayscale output
	bug fix: for single page input pdf, output file renamed, not deleted
	argument -units PixelsPerInch added to convert
	command line argument order for convert changed according to recommendations
	OpenBSD support added for guessing number of processors

create_torrent 0.1.5 (Thu, 04 Aug 2016 14:31:28 +0200):
	gs mostly replaced by pdfinfo and pdfunite from poppler-utils
	new options -pdfinfo and -pdfunite for the respective binaries

create_torrent 0.1.4 (Thu, 09 Jul 2015 12:31:28 +0200):
	bugfix: keep original extension of input file
	display warning if tesseract does not support option -list_langs

create_torrent 0.1.3 (Sat, 09 Aug 2014 19:33:04 +0200):
	make the default preprocessing options more conservative
	add useful preprocessing options, such as -layout
	set page size of OCR'd pdf to original pdf page size
	allow manual output page size settings by option -pagesize
	option -list_langs to list languages available on the system

create_torrent 0.1.2 (Thu, 24 Jul 2014 14:32:50 +0200):
	bugfix in detection of tesseract >= 3.03

